## Session start (this home only)

1. Last block of `SESSION_HANDOFF.md`
2. `.agents/memory/MEMORY.md` (CONFIRMED_FACTS, LEARNED_RULES)
3. This file if roles/rules changed

**Do not expect** (not installed in lite): `STATUS.md`, program `SPEC.md`, `waves/`, `prompts/_dispatch/`.

